uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T06:34:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雜棋王會捉輸棋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比啲時間棋王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n棋王捉緊一盤好大嘅棋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627c27b1701f4aaab1b3064c8f4960404c4ddc00","tid":233040,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T06:34:30.000Z","msg":"侵侵唔郁金仔住，就係等呢啲機會。啱啱揸住中共春袋，未部處好，郁金仔無著數，隨時俾大陸佬執二攤。而家迫雜種同金仔反面，等北泡人民憎鳩大陸佬，跟住先倒金仔台，到時大陸佬就想偷雞控權就難得多。"},{"pid":"ca1348d2a8d1cc161180c3f6954453de656c2b46","tid":233040,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T06:37:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>侵侵唔郁金仔住，就係等呢啲機會。啱啱揸住中共春袋，未部處好，郁金仔無著數，隨時俾大陸佬執二攤。而家迫雜種同金仔反面，等北泡人民憎鳩大陸佬，跟住先倒金仔台，到時大陸佬就想偷雞控權就難得多。</blockquote><br />\n撚狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef94a17c798cc5a131626c9e7dad133b35e455d","tid":233040,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那而家連唯一表面盟友都冇埋<br />\n俾侵侵撚2野就搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話自己大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n習總捉棋好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}